*** Loch Long
*** Loch Fyne, Scotland&#x27;s longest fjord at 65 km
*** Loch Etive
** Sweden
*** Gullmarsfjorden, in Bohuslän, Sweden
** Wales
*** Mawddach Estuary, a fjord in-filled by glacial deposits.
* North America
** Canada:
*** the west and south coasts of Newfoundland, particularly:
**** Facheux Bay
**** Bonne Bay in Gros Morne National Park
**** Aviron Bay
**** La Hune Bay
**** Bay de Vieux
**** White Bear Bay
**** Baie d&#x27;Espoir
**** La Poile Bay
**** Bay Le Moine
*** the Canadian Arctic Archipelago
